iz er gegan, ⟨ts-⟩ keyn ⟨PALAP⟩.

00:10:15.882 --> 00:10:17.884
er hot im untergetsundn di klinye,

00:10:18.227 --> 00:10:18.980
un er hot

00:10:18.278 --> 00:10:19.352
ver, Yidl?

00:10:19.172 --> 00:10:20.836
neyn, neyn! Meyer.

00:10:20.353 --> 00:10:22.151
ah, nokh Meyer, far dem.

00:10:21.231 --> 00:10:23.870
yo, Meyer! er hot zikh zikh nokh gelebt a yor tsayt.

00:10:23.870 --> 00:10:25.817
Yidl nisht. Yidl iz nisht geven ⟨keyn tuer⟩ oyf dem.

00:10:24.808 --> 00:10:25.848
⟨kh'⟩farshtey.

00:10:25.817 --> 00:10:26.338
yo.

00:10:26.850 --> 00:10:28.780
in im hot gebrent der kaas,

00:10:28.780 --> 00:10:31.471
⟨er, az er⟩ hot gedorfn iberlozn aza kind fun, fun,

00:10:31.471 --> 00:10:33.881
fun dray yor. a velt ⟨sheynheyt⟩ iz dos geven!

00:10:35.187 --> 00:10:37.057
un er hot untergetsundn di klinye,

00:10:37.057 --> 00:10:41.323
un er hot im arayngeshosn in shtub arayn, nor er hot im nisht getrofn, un er iz avek.

00:10:41.903 --> 00:10:47.392
er iz avek, un er iz avek keyn Kosnishtsh un er hot gebitn dem plats. dos iz shoyn geven der,

00:10:47.392 --> 00:10:52.404
⟨der, der,⟩ dos iz shoyn geven dos letste optu zayns. dos iz shoyn geven in a yor arum, in tsvey un fertsikstn,

00:10:52.404 --> 00:10:55.898
un in dray un fertsikstn iz er gegan UNK ⟨im untertsindn⟩, tsum yor.

00:10:55.898 --> 00:10:57.000
punkt tsum yor.

00:10:57.057 --> 00:11:00.281
dernokh m'hot zey aroysgenumen dort, dem, di, di,

00:11:00.381 --> 00:11:03.615
gehargete aroysgenumen, ibergefirt oyfn heylikn ort.

00:11:02.237 --> 00:11:05.842
d- ayer gevezener man, der frierdiker man oykhet dortn iz ge⟨UNK⟩?

00:11:04.802 --> 00:11:09.766
yo. hot men aroysgenumen im mit, mit der shvegerin, mitn kind, mit der khavertorin.

00:11:09.766 --> 00:11:11.574
m'hot zey ibergefirt oyfn heylikn ort.

00:11:11.574 --> 00:11:16.051
un dernokh di tsvey brider fun Kosnishtsh oykhet aroysgenumen un ibergefirt oyfn heylikn ort.

00:11:16.142 --> 00:11:19.460
un, mit dem hot zikh geendikt di ale ts-, tsores.

00:11:18.876 --> 00:11:22.768
heyst dos, in Libevne nokhn bafrayen zent ir geblibn biz velkhn yor?

00:11:22.892 --> 00:11:25.468
bizn, zeks un fertsikstn yor.

00:11:25.052 --> 00:11:29.278
un in Libevne hot ir khasene gehat. ir hot getrofn a, a...

00:11:26.993 --> 00:11:31.877
⟨in⟩ Libevne... in Libevne, ⟨yo, hob ikh gornisht⟩ geklert shoyn khasene tsu hobn, nor

00:11:31.877 --> 00:11:34.895
kh'hob zikh opgegebn nor tsu di kinder vayl kh'hob gehat aza mitleyd mit zey.

00:11:34.895 --> 00:11:38.979
kh'hob zey gebodn un gevashn bay tog un bay nakht un gekokht di esns.

00:11:38.979 --> 00:11:42.832
un, biz vanet kh'hob zey geshtelt oyf di fis. az zey hobn zikh geshtelt oyf di fis,

00:11:43.108 --> 00:11:48.070
hob ikh gezen azoy az, oder ikh darf zikh UNK veynen un klogn, bay tog un bay nakht,

00:11:48.070 --> 00:11:49.956
un ale hobn ongehoybn tsu tun mit mir,

00:11:49.956 --> 00:11:53.196
oder ordenen zikh ayn. dervayl iz aropgekumen mayn man, er zol zayn gezunt,

00:11:53.196 --> 00:11:56.298
vos, kh'hob im gekent, ⟨fun avoser⟩ mishpokhe er iz.

00:11:56.406 --> 00:12:01.175
er iz aropgekumen zukhn mishpokhe. dervayl zenen mir shoyn, azoy iz er farblibn, un azoy hobn mir zikh farbundn.

00:12:01.333 --> 00:12:05.664
⟨, oyf tsu⟩ forn keyn Poyln bald ⟨un m-⟩ nor m'iz nisht geforn, m'iz farblibn azoy.

00:12:05.029 --> 00:12:08.246
zent ir fun Libevne aribergeforn koydem keyn Lemberg?

00:12:06.818 --> 00:12:08.516
keyn Lemberg, yo.

00:12:08.657 --> 00:12:11.789
dertseylt a bisl dos lebn in Lemberg.

00:12:10.007 --> 00:12:14.796
yo, aribergeforn keyn Lemberg. m'hot dortn zikh ayngeordnt. der man hot gearbet,

00:12:14.796 --> 00:12:16.784
als a ongeshtelter in a gevelb

00:12:17.027 --> 00:12:20.773
un ikh ho- ⟨,⟩ geborn di tsvey kinder, zoln zayn gezunt,

00:12:20.773 --> 00:12:22.961
un gehaltn di tsvey kinder bay zikh.

00:12:23.187 --> 00:12:25.796
un di tsvey kinder hob ikh gelernt.

00:12:24.402 --> 00:12:26.472
un der bruder, vu iz er geven demlt?

00:12:25.796 --> 00:12:27.349
der bruder iz geven in Libevne.

00:12:26.999 --> 00:12:28.580
⟨ah, er⟩ hot geblibn in Libevne.

00:12:27.878 --> 00:12:30.285
yo, un di kinder zenen geven mit mir.

00:12:30.308 --> 00:12:35.584
ikh, de- in Lemberik, yeder hot gemeynt az mayn man iz der foter fun zey. m'hot zey gehaltn zeyer gut.

00:12:35.607 --> 00:12:37.586
⟨d-⟩ di, zey hobn gelernt.

00:12:37.586 --> 00:12:42.182
