00:12:45.985 --> 00:12:46.941
⟨zen-⟩

00:12:48.222 --> 00:12:50.939
m'hot ⟨azoy⟩ zikh ayngeshtelt. a kosher lebn hot men nisht gekent.

00:12:50.939 --> 00:12:53.640
me hot ⟨zikh⟩ gemuzt aynshteln oyfn, oyf der parnose.

00:12:53.292 --> 00:12:56.495
geblibn in Lemberg zent ir bizn zibn un fuftsikstn?

00:12:55.418 --> 00:12:58.534
⟨⟩, zibn un fuftsikstn yor, ven es iz aroysgekumen dos forn,

00:12:56.852 --> 00:12:57.892
⟨hob ikh⟩

00:12:58.573 --> 00:13:01.295
zenen mir avekgeforn keyn, Varshe.

00:12:59.940 --> 00:13:01.064
keyn Poyln.

00:13:01.295 --> 00:13:03.953
keyn Poyln. fun Varshe zenen mir ongekumen aher

00:13:03.953 --> 00:13:06.363
dem fiftn may, ⟨dem⟩ zibn un fuftsikstn yor.

00:13:07.129 --> 00:13:09.873
lebndik in LV- Lemberg

00:13:10.015 --> 00:13:13.892
fun zeks un fertsik biz zibn un fuftsik unter di sovyetishe regi-

00:13:13.525 --> 00:13:14.464
yo.

00:13:13.892 --> 00:13:17.467
regirung, hot ir shoyn mir gezogt, s'iz geven a shrek un m'hot zikh gedarft dreyen...

00:13:16.545 --> 00:13:17.855
yo.

00:13:17.710 --> 00:13:20.589
akhuts dem, antisemitishkeyt iz geven dortn?

00:13:20.646 --> 00:13:23.795
s'iz geven. s'hot nisht gefelt dort, di antisemitn.

00:13:22.350 --> 00:13:24.892
oykhet un- afile unter ⟨di sovyetishe tsaytn⟩?

00:13:23.802 --> 00:13:27.258
yo! s'iz nokh geven. s'iz geven. di sovyetn, s'iz geven. di,

00:13:27.025 --> 00:13:28.573
di ukrainer dort?

