di, di ukrainer dort, di same UNK dort iz ⟨dokh⟩ di same natsyonalistn. yo!

00:13:30.062 --> 00:13:31.869
di natsyonalistn.

00:13:32.278 --> 00:13:36.176
⟨undz ho'mir⟩ gevoynt, eyn yidishe familye dort oyf der B⟨UNK⟩INER gas,

00:13:36.176 --> 00:13:40.496
