00:13:40.496 --> 00:13:44.622
vi azoy zey hobn zikh moy- noykem geven in di yidn, ven di ts-, ven di daytshn zenen arayn,

00:13:44.622 --> 00:13:46.453
hobn zey genumen akht tog fray

00:13:46.453 --> 00:13:50.140
un zey hobn, zey hobn, zey, zey, un zey hobn geshosn di yidn.

00:13:49.249 --> 00:13:51.136
gesht⟨UNK⟩n di yidn.

00:13:50.140 --> 00:13:50.981
⟨okh⟩!

00:13:51.136 --> 00:13:54.215
yetst, ir't ongekumen keyn Varshe in zibn un fuftsik,

00:13:53.805 --> 00:13:54.727
yo.

00:13:54.215 --> 00:13:57.664
⟨un⟩ a kurtse tsayt zayendik in Varshe hot ir ⟨zikh⟩...

00:13:56.404 --> 00:13:58.608
in Varshe zenen mir geven nisht lang,

00:13:58.969 --> 00:14:02.619
un m'iz gekumen, zenen mir geven in Italye dray vokhn.

00:14:02.619 --> 00:14:05.903
fun Italye zenen mir gekumen, ⟨ot aher⟩.

00:14:05.903 --> 00:14:08.379
un m'hot gekrign ⟨glaykh KHULON⟩ fun der shif.

00:14:08.824 --> 00:14:11.298
m'hot gekrign a ⟨TSERIF⟩ UNK.

00:14:11.440 --> 00:14:13.357
un fun der shif,

00:14:13.532 --> 00:14:16.327
un do hot men zikh shoyn azoy gematert. m'hot zikh ⟨ge-⟩

00:14:15.338 --> 00:14:19.534
yetst, onkumendik take in land, in zibn un fuftsik, mit tsvey meydlekh,

00:14:18.021 --> 00:14:18.892
yo.

00:14:19.152 --> 00:14:20.074
yo.

00:14:19.793 --> 00:14:22.107
di kinder, Yidl's kin-

00:14:20.485 --> 00:14:22.639
di kinder zenen alt geven,

00:14:22.107 --> 00:14:25.929
zenen gekumen mit aykh di, Yidl's kinder zenen oykhet gekumen mit aykh do in land ⟨dan⟩?

00:14:24.653 --> 00:14:29.360
der, der yingl iz gekumen glaykh mit mir. ⟨di t-⟩ meydl hot shoyn gehat dort khasene gehat,

00:14:26.509 --> 00:14:28.145
di meydl, ⟨vu iz⟩...

00:14:28.618 --> 00:14:29.523
aha.

00:14:29.360 --> 00:14:30.941
iz zi gekumen shpeter

00:14:30.745 --> 00:14:33.523
yo. un ⟨ven s'- u- u- ⟩ un der bruder?

00:14:31.352 --> 00:14:33.101
mit der familye.

00:14:33.445 --> 00:14:35.905
un der bruder iz gekumen nokh shpeter.

00:14:35.905 --> 00:14:36.661
yo.

00:14:36.600 --> 00:14:38.416
⟨er iz⟩ gekumen oykh in land arayn?

00:14:37.545 --> 00:14:38.788
yo. yo.

00:14:38.845 --> 00:14:42.786
iz vi, dertseylt a bisl di shverikeyt, vi ir hot zikh do ayngeordnt,

00:14:42.786 --> 00:14:44.778
mitn man, mit di kinder in ⟨KHULON⟩.

00:14:43.620 --> 00:14:49.250
nu, m'iz gekumen ot o do. m'hot gekrign dem ⟨TSERIF⟩. s'iz nisht geven laykht, vayl keyn fakh iz nisht gevezn,

00:14:49.527 --> 00:14:54.043
un mayn man iz gezitsn a yor tsayt on arbet. ikh bin gegan arbetn in a fabrik fun bikher.

00:14:54.657 --> 00:15:00.624
un di kinder hobn gelernt, UNK zey hobn gelernt zeyer gut. zey hobn gekhapt di shprakh zeyer shnel

00:15:00.850 --> 00:15:02.784
un zey zenen gegan zeyer foroys.

00:15:03.617 --> 00:15:09.601
un, dernokh, mayn man hot gearbet bay a khaver, bay elektrishe lompn.

00:15:10.215 --> 00:15:15.339
un azoy hot men gearbet biz vanet... dernokh hot men gemakht, zelbshtendik gevorn, m'hot zikh gemakht a vesheray.

00:15:15.565 --> 00:15:17.904
m'hot opgearbet zeyer shver un,

00:15:18.484 --> 00:15:20.047
 ⟨b-⟩ biz

00:15:19.058 --> 00:15:21.418
⟨do-⟩ biz m'iz aroys oyf pensye.

00:15:20.138 --> 00:15:25.363
biz vanet m'iz aroys oyf pensye. ⟨nu, m'iz nokh⟩ aroys far der pensye, vayl s'hot zikh gemakht,

00:15:25.234 --> 00:15:26.443
yetst azoy.

00:15:25.825 --> 00:15:27.793
⟨vil⟩ nisht dermanen dem fal.

00:15:26.854 --> 00:15:28.586
yo. hot ir

00:15:28.710 --> 00:15:33.716
a eltere tokhter, un ir hot a tsveyte tokhter. vi heyst zi, ⟨ELA⟩?

00:15:32.845 --> 00:15:33.952
⟨ELA⟩.

00:15:34.262 --> 00:15:37.546
vos iz farheyrat gega- zi hot khasene gehat.

00:15:35.713 --> 00:15:36.635
yo.

00:15:37.063 --> 00:15:38.684
zi hot khasene gehat un

00:15:37.603 --> 00:15:39.318
ir hot dray eyniklekh?

00:15:38.684 --> 00:15:42.929
⟨zi hot⟩ dray eyniklekh un zi arbet, ales advokat, un,

00:15:43.206 --> 00:15:44.803
un zi firt ir lebn.

00:15:45.332 --> 00:15:47.840
⟨un do- dos i-⟩ zi firt ir lebn.

00:15:47.475 --> 00:15:50.135
yetst hob ikh aykh gevolt fregn nokh a frage.

00:15:51.610 --> 00:15:53.528
lebndik do in land,

00:15:54.310 --> 00:15:56.568
flegt ir dertseyln di kinder

00:15:56.568 --> 00:15:58.657
vos mit aykh es hot ongegangen?

00:15:56.605 --> 00:16:01.120
alts dertseylt. nokh in Rusland hob ikh zey dertseylt. zey hobn ales gevust.

00:16:01.120 --> 00:16:04.001
nisht azoy vi andere eltern, me fartayet, me vil nisht dertseyln.

00:16:03.912 --> 00:16:05.161
⟨hobn⟩

00:16:04.001 --> 00:16:07.916
ikh hob zey ales dertseylt. zey veysn di historye fun der gantser mishpokhe.

00:16:07.708 --> 00:16:10.199
di eyniklekh oykhet flegn zikh interesirn?

00:16:07.916 --> 00:16:08.799
vos...

00:16:09.261 --> 00:16:11.910
di eyniklekh, zenen zikh nokh, nor,

00:16:10.881 --> 00:16:12.090
nokh kleyne?

00:16:11.910 --> 00:16:13.673
nor zey veysn. ot fregt zi,

00:16:13.673 --> 00:16:17.692
az zey zenen nokh geven kleyn, fregt zi, "ver iz JANUSZ KORCZAK?" ⟨un azoy veysn⟩, vu ⟨iz⟩ der,

00:16:17.692 --> 00:16:20.707
vu ⟨iz⟩ der zeyde mit der babe veysn zey. alts veysn zey.

00:16:20.707 --> 00:16:24.015
ot, a shteyger, di eltere tokhter, ven zi iz geborn gevorn in Lemberg,

00:16:24.015 --> 00:16:27.864
es iz geven rusishe kinder, vos zey hobn gehat zeydes mit babes. zi hot nisht gehat.

00:16:27.864 --> 00:16:30.922
