00:16:33.325 --> 00:16:34.348
⟨⟩.

00:16:36.941 --> 00:16:40.254
UNK s'iz nishto keyn DEDUSHKA. s'iz nishto keyn BABUSHKA.

00:16:40.193 --> 00:16:41.720
⟨farshtey⟩.

00:16:40.328 --> 00:16:42.904
un azoy, un azoy hobn zey zikh tsugevoynt dertsu.

00:16:43.045 --> 00:16:48.841
un di kinder veysn alts. zey, kleyne kinder, zey zogn nokh, di yingelekh, zogn az zey viln nokh forn keyn Kovle, keyn Libevne

00:16:48.841 --> 00:16:50.731
un zen vu m'iz geborn gevorn.

00:16:50.731 --> 00:16:54.480
un der kleyner zogt, "di daytshn," zogt er... er iz in kaas oyf di daytshn shreklekh.

00:16:54.537 --> 00:16:55.442
yo.

00:16:54.958 --> 00:16:57.722
yetst ayer man, zol zayn gezunt,

00:16:57.722 --> 00:17:00.537
er iz geven in Rusland, in rusishn militer?

00:16:59.295 --> 00:17:00.994
er iz geven in der armey,

00:17:00.994 --> 00:17:01.601
yo.

00:17:01.708 --> 00:17:05.600
er iz oykhet a Kovler. vos iz geshen mit zayn mishpokhe? oykhet umgekumen?

00:17:02.822 --> 00:17:05.014
er iz a Kovler ⟨geborener⟩.

00:17:05.014 --> 00:17:09.754
umgekumen, di gantse mishpokhe. er eyner iz geven farnumen in TSAVA, in, militer,

00:17:09.754 --> 00:17:11.876
iz er eyner al-pi nes geblibn.

00:17:11.876 --> 00:17:14.009
⟨m'hot⟩ di gantse mishpokhe umgekumen.

00:17:14.415 --> 00:17:18.172
gantse mishpokhe. ⟨s'iz⟩ geven a groyse mishpokhe. ⟨a gantse⟩ UNK

