00:17:20.540 --> 00:17:23.262
kh'hob ⟨nokh⟩ gevolt dertseyln a bisl fun di shkheynim,

00:17:22.954 --> 00:17:24.061
yo, bite.

00:17:23.262 --> 00:17:25.364
vos zenen geblibn on,

00:17:24.979 --> 00:17:25.952
dertseylt.

00:17:25.364 --> 00:17:27.570
on a zeykher, on a zeykher.

00:17:26.093 --> 00:17:28.112
bite, bite dertseylt.

00:17:27.570 --> 00:17:30.165
s'iz geven bay undz, zeyer, zeyer fayne shkheynim.

00:17:30.165 --> 00:17:33.097
s'iz geven a, a shokhn akegn, Moyshe Notl,

00:17:33.097 --> 00:17:36.653
vos ⟨er⟩ iz geven ale yorn, ⟨er iz geven⟩ a gevir, un er iz geven a gabe fun a shil,

00:17:36.653 --> 00:17:41.555
un, a mol az s'iz geven a telefon ⟨in der⟩ shtub, in yene yorn iz dos geven a luksus.

00:17:41.555 --> 00:17:43.875
un a shi- un a dinst hobn zey gehaltn.

00:17:43.875 --> 00:17:47.771
ikh bin MAMASH, shtendik geshlofn bay zey, vayl bay undz iz geven eyn tsimer.

00:17:47.811 --> 00:17:50.457
eyn tsimer iz geven fun, ⟨, n-,⟩ nayn kinder!

00:17:50.457 --> 00:17:53.889
di eltere kinder zenen take khasene ⟨gehat un zenen zikh⟩ tsegan, ober dernokh

00:17:53.889 --> 00:17:55.970
iz men geblibn finef kinder in shtub.

00:17:55.970 --> 00:17:57.556
⟨ikh gedenk nokh, ven m'iz geshlofn a⟩,

00:17:57.556 --> 00:18:00.949
eyner oyf a kufert, eyner oyf a pekele ⟨kart- azoy iz dos gegangen⟩,

00:18:00.949 --> 00:18:02.705
dos lebn inem kleynem shtetele.

00:18:04.838 --> 00:18:11.430
⟨ot azoy iz⟩, zenen geven, zenen geven zeyer raykhe mentshn. dernokh, ven s'iz arayn di sovyetn hot men zey, ⟨hot zey aroys⟩ UNK⟨et⟩.

00:18:11.430 --> 00:18:13.010
s'iz ⟨nokh⟩ geven dem letstn shabes,

00:18:13.010 --> 00:18:16.172
bin ikh geshtanen lebn im bay der shtub. zogt er, "du veyst?" zogt er,

00:18:16.212 --> 00:18:20.053
 "loz shoyn zayn a milkhome. abi d- abi di ⟨borveses⟩ zoln shoyn aroys.

